Yes, production sent us videos with several proposals and that was the band we liked the most, so we look forward to seeing what Las Robertas can offer live and should be very entertaining.
Why do Yellow Ledbetter's lyrics always change live?
That's a question for Ed (Eddie Vedder), so I don't know.
